# Heavier pre-push gate: type-check, lint, and test the active apps (+ their deps).
# Turbo caching makes unchanged packages instant. Full build + security scans run in CI.
#
# Mirrors CI: the desktop-v2 APP's lint + type-check are report-only for now (main's WIP
# online-store feature has pre-existing errors). Everything else is blocking.
set -e

# Blocking: api + all shared packages (incl. desktop-v2's deps, via `desktop-v2^...`).
pnpm turbo run type-check lint test --filter=@biztrack/api... --filter=@biztrack/desktop-v2^...

# Blocking: desktop-v2 app tests.
pnpm turbo run test --filter=@biztrack/desktop-v2

# Report-only: desktop-v2 app lint + type-check.
pnpm turbo run lint type-check --filter=@biztrack/desktop-v2 || true
